node.text:
Do you adore the look of purple flowers? We definitely do! 🌺⁠
⁠
⁠"𝐀𝐮𝐭𝐨 𝐁𝐥𝐚𝐜𝐤𝐛𝐞𝐫𝐫𝐲 𝐊𝐮𝐬𝐡 is quite a strong and forgiving autoflower. These plants had to endure a severe pest outbreak during their early growth stages and still came out very strong! Nutrient wise she was very straightforward, not a fussy eater at all.⁠
⁠
All in all a beautiful purple autoflowering strain with a strong aroma and taste." 💜⁠ ⁠
⁠
👨🏻‍🌾 Grown by Sticky Green of the Urban Growers Collective (@ugc.official) ⁠
📸 These beautiful pictures were taken by @antonioo_cc⁠
🔗 Full report - link in our bio⁠
⁠
#blackberry #purple #purpleflowers #colours #prettyinpurple #nature #naturephotography #greenthumb #strong #forgiving

node.text:
Hydroponics is a type of horticulture used for growing. Specifically, hydroponics is a form of hydro culture which involves growing plants/crops without soil. Instead the mineral content of the nutrient solution provides the necessary food for plant growth. ⁠
⁠
The majority of varieties will grow well in hydroponic conditions. But which seeds will really shine in a hydroponic grow and why? 💧⁠
⁠
📘 Read more in our blog: Top 5 seeds to grow in hydroponics⁠
🔗 Link in our bio & story⁠
⁠
#hydroponics #hydroponicsystem #hydro #hydroculture #blog #happyfriday #fridaynight

What a beautiful bouquet of 𝐆𝐥𝐮𝐞𝐛𝐞𝐫𝐫𝐲 𝐎𝐆 flowers! ⁠💐⁠
⁠
"Her flowers are fluffy and bright with a neon green coloring that’s accented by orange hairs and a coating of tiny white crystals. Just as you’d guess, blueberry flavor is prominent as you 𝚜𝚖𝚘𝚔𝚎, and this note is complemented by diesel, spice, and wood for a robust and complex taste and strong 𝙺𝚞𝚜𝚑 aroma."⁠ - 💬 Comment by the grower @thecannaprophet2.0⁠
⁠
#bouquet #green #gardening #happy #blueberry #diesel #spice #wood #complextaste

node.text:
𝐀𝐮𝐭𝐨 𝐌𝐚𝐳𝐚𝐫 was one of the first from Dutch Passion to be developed during the emergence of the 𝚊𝚞𝚝𝚘𝚏𝚕𝚘𝚠𝚎𝚛 𝚜𝚝𝚛𝚊𝚒𝚗𝚜 in the 𝚌𝚊𝚗𝚗𝚊𝚋𝚒𝚜 𝚠𝚘𝚛𝚕𝚍. 🌱⁠
⁠
At the time there was a fear among growers that autoflowers were not good enough to compete with photoperiod plants. Our 𝐀𝐮𝐭𝐨 𝐌𝐚𝐳𝐚𝐫 immediately made this a thing of the past. 💪⁠
⁠
📸 On these pictures, you see some different 𝐀𝐮𝐭𝐨 𝐌𝐚𝐳𝐚𝐫 phenos grown by @basement.trees⁠
🔗 More info - link in our bio⁠
⁠
#phenos #phenotypes #plants #plantsofinstagram #plantsmakepeoplehappy

𝐇𝐢𝐅𝐢 𝟒𝐆 is known for her exceptional vigor and her sturdy thick branches. During the growth phase she seems to grow a bit faster than most hybrid strains. Even the stems of the leaves are firmer and thicker than usual. 🍀⁠
⁠
👨‍🌾 This stunner was grown by @trichome_medical ⁠

node.text:
Did you know? 🤔⁠
⁠
The total number of coffee shops in the Netherlands decreased by 21% from 2005 to 2019.⁠ 📉⁠
⁠
📷 On the 15th of March 2020, the Dutch government announced new measures to contain the coronavirus, which included the closure of restaurants, bars, clubs, gyms and coffee shops. Unsurprisingly, people then queued up in long lines at the coffee shops, as you can see on this picture.⁠
⁠
#dutchpassiondidyouknow #didyouknow #funfact #picoftheday

node.text:
The Ultimate is perhaps Dutch Passion’s all-time 𝚑𝚎𝚊𝚟𝚒𝚎𝚜𝚝 𝚢𝚒𝚎𝚕𝚍𝚒𝚗𝚐 𝚟𝚊𝚛𝚒𝚎𝚝𝚢! ⚖️ ⁠
⁠
The Ultimate is a powerful balanced hybrid which produces massive blooms that can easily grow as thick as your forearm. 🙌⁠
⁠
"The 5 plants 𝕪𝕚𝕖𝕝𝕕𝕖𝕕 close to 600g of dried flowers with 420+60 = 480watts of LED light. Organically grown without the use of any CO2 or other additives, we were highly impressed." - 💬 Comment by the growers @antonioo_cc and Fernando from the Urban Growers Collective (@ugc.official)⁠ 👨‍🌾⁠
⁠
🔗 Read the full report - link in our bio ⁠
⁠
#ultimate #saturday #weekend #saturyay #postivevibes #feelgood

node.text:
C𝕒𝕟𝕟𝕒𝕓𝕚𝕤 is particularly pungent and aromatic when dried/cured. Most people describe the 𝕔𝕒𝕟𝕟𝕒𝕓𝕚𝕤 aroma as earthy, woody and herbal. It’s difficult to define precisely, but the iconic and characteristic scent is often easy to notice. 👃🌱⁠
⁠
How would you describe the smell? ⁠💨⁠
⁠
📖 Read our blog to learn more about the individual component smells and how to maximise the smell.⁠
🔗 Link in our bio & story⁠
⁠
#smell #aroma #pungent #earthy #woody #herbal #herbs #blog

⁠𝔸𝕦𝕥𝕠 ℂ𝕚𝕟𝕕𝕖𝕣𝕖𝕝𝕝𝕒 𝕁𝕒𝕔𝕜 is strong and compact and filled from head to toe with sticky flowers with a good flower-to-leaf ratio. 🌻🌿⁠

⁠
